page_title: 'How to generate text with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Learn how to generate or manipulate text, including code by using a completion endpoint in Azure OpenAI Service.
chunk_content: Work with codeThe Codex model series is a descendant of OpenAI's base GPT-3 series that's been trained on both natural language and billions of lines of code. It's most capable in Python and proficient in over a dozen languages including C#, JavaScript, Go, Perl, PHP, Ruby, Swift, TypeScript, SQL, and even Shell. For more information about generating code completions, see Codex models and Azure OpenAI Service.
